node.text:
I wanted to celebrate three years in business in a proper Josie way 💥 🔥 😂 Thank you for all your amazing support and I’m honoured I get to be apart of your day 🌈 

Hope I made you smile 😃 
Love Sweet Josie 

P.S @livstagrammin and @jocelynmercer11 should this be my meet the teacher video 😂 I feel like it explains everything you need to know about my teaching style 😂 😂

node.text: First voice over video and it was so much harder then I thought it was going to be 😂 But I gave myself a deadline to post one and of course I waited until the last day to get my nerves up to do it 🤗 but I’m happy I finally did one 😃 let me know in the comments if you want another voice over video

#sweetapolita #wiltoncakes #chocolatecake #pinkcakes #caketopper #cake #cakes #prettycake #cakesofinstagram #howto #butter #buttercream #cakedecorating #baker #cakedesign #cakesofinsta #cakestagram #cakecakecake #instacolor #colorright #buzzfeedfood #buzzfeed #cakeoftheday

The only downfall in learning how to make artisan chocolate 🍫 is you now know how to make addictive chocolates in under an hour 😂 your tummy will thank you but your bum 🍑 and hips will not haha 😂 I regret nothing !!! 

Link in bio to make these together today!! See you in class 🤗

node.text: Spooky but make it cute ☺️ 👻 I used a acetate sheet and a X-Acto knife to create my own stencil! I’m thinking of doing this again but with some 3D bats and sprinkles 🤩

Every Halloween I make a different version of a “slime” cake ( like the stuff they used to dump on you during that nickelodeon TV show 😂 I’m old, does anyone else remember that??) 

Can’t wait to remake this cake again and see what different design I can come up with ! Do you like recreating old cakes  and which is your favourite? 🤗
